products.title: Azurite Chenille Grey Roman Blind
products.description: Their azurite chenille range consists of textured plains with a velour soft-feel finish. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, which is why this roman comes with their free five year guarantee and customer-first service. Available as a matching curtain.
